    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_PersonalizationPerUser_SetPageSettings",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to manage user-specific personalization settings for web applications. It associates personalization data with a specific user and page path within an application. The procedure ensures that the application, path, and user exist in the database, creating them if necessary, and then updates or inserts the personalization settings for the user-page combination."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple steps, including checking and creating records in different tables, updating user activity, and managing personalization data. The complexity arises from the need to handle multiple entities (applications, paths, users) and ensure data integrity across these entities."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@ApplicationName NVARCHAR(256)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The name of the application for which personalization settings are being managed."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@UserName NVARCHAR(256)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The username of the user whose personalization settings are being updated."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@Path NVARCHAR(256)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The path within the application that the personalization settings apply to."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@PageSettings IMAGE",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The personalization settings data, stored as an image type, which is used for binary data."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@CurrentTimeUtc DATETIME",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The current UTC time, used for timestamping updates and user activity."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
